subproject.description:
1.	Process for ICT companies in order to get established, operate and  develop innovative ideas in Egypt facilitated 
2.	Assisted foreign and local ICT companies to create, enrich and expand innovative jobs
3.	Building Egypt’s external brand in ICT innovation
4.	Engaging  Egyptian society in supporting and using ICT related innovations.
subproject.title: Supporting TIEC Activities

subproject.corporate outcome: Enhanced national capacity to use ICT for development as driver for pro-poor capacity development and institutional building
